    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/cityinn-plus-taichung-station-branch/hotel/taichung-tw.html",
    "name": "CityInn Plus Taichung Station Branch",
    "detail": "i recently enjoyed a weekend stay in this brand new hotel after staying in a sister hotel in downtown taipei. the rooms in taichung are larger, very stylish with different themes on many of the floors. mine was a sports theme and it made the stay even more interesting. excellent facilities in the hotel and room, including laundry facilities, a super rain shower, toiletries and free video on demand. staff are very helpful and polite, english was not a problem and everything was explained clearly. free wifi throughout. breakfast was one of the best i've had for a medium sized hotel, high quality, fresh, and regularly restocked. most importantly it's in an excellent location behind the train station, literally three minutes from the tracks but no noise disturbance at all. across the road is a brand new shopping mall complex, and taxi and bus stands are right outside the door. definitely my new 'to-go-to' hotel in taichung.",
